HOW IS THE GENOCIDE NOTED?    HIJACKING & KILLING OF       INDIANS AS WELL AS OTHER BLACK & BROWN SKINNED PEOPLE    ……all over the place in the Western & Asian Countries 
PROCESS BEGINS WITH AN INVITATION-by someone from your circle of friends, relatives & colleagues to go out to place to eat OR to shop OR visit a friend OR go for a sleep over OR a Party OR a movie, etc, etc.  You will be taken to 1or 2 places & then you will be walked / driven to some place, where you will be left, while your friend / relative will sneak out.  There is no way, you will be allowed to come out & finally you will NOT BE SEEN AGAIN.
TIPS FOR SAFETY- WHEN MEETING PEOPLE & GOING OUT
When you are invited by friends & relatives to go out – it is best to not agree until you have more information, such as:    Where are we going?   What are we going to do?  What time?   Once you find out the place, if it is not a big Mall, Superstore or a popular Restaurant, propose to meet in a Mall.  If the person agrees, then you follow the steps given below –                                                                                    
• You should NOT TRAVEL in THEIR VEHICLE …Travel independently to GO meet people.  
• After meeting WITH PEOPLE in the Mall, GO ABOUT YOUR OWN WAYS SEPARATELY as well as without informing the people of where you are going.  
• NEVER TAG with PEOPLE.  It means DO NOT GO with people from Mall to a Function or to another 
Store or to someone’s home etc, etc, even if it is A MUST.  Going from place to place, will eventually take you to the place of Extermination       *    When Travelling take busy roads.

DRIVING:   BASED ON OBSERVATIONS & STATEMENTS FROM PEOPLE, it is concluded:  (i)   Do Not Follow vehicles of friends & relatives.  It is noted you may get taken outside the major city limits where unwanted scenarios may have been set up & organized.  It is best for you to PLAN YOUR OWN ROUTES for travelling   (ii)   BE ATTENTIVE WHEN DRIVING – Based on observations & statements reported, vehicles make intentional changes in the path of THEIR driving towards your vehicle such that there are collisions, especially if you are brown & black skinned individual..   
WALKING ON THE STREETS:   It is OBSERVED & REPORTED, THAT there are several Vehicles of Strangers moving around the streets who are monitoring people on the streets.  The minute you are spotted as one of the wanted kinds (brown OR black skinned), the Vehicle parks away from the mainstream of crowd & the driver then follows behind the pedestrian & will seize the opportunity to grab & drag/lead the individual to his /her vehicle.
WHEN CROSSING THE STREETS:   It is reported & observed that vehicles come out of nowhere & move in the direction of the pedestrian crossing the street to strike them down on the street so that the pedestrian is severely injured.    Therefore, it is NOT ONLY important to watch Right, Left, Front but also at the back of where you are standing when crossing, all the time 
SHOPPING:  It is observed & reported that Shopping Carts loaded with groceries get snatched from the hands of people coming out of the Grocery Stores and the person who snatches the cart, then walks faster & QUIETLY or may say loudly, “Honey, our car is at the back, common this way follow me”.  This method is just to bring you away from the crowd so that they are able to grab you & take you away in his / her car.   So, YELL FOR HELP BUT DO NOT COME CLOSE TO THE PERSON WHO HAS YOUR CART.  IF THERE IS NO HELP AVAILABLE, IT IS BEST, TO LET GO YOUR CART & SAFEGUARD YOURSELF.
WORSHIP PLACES:   DO NOT TAKE RIDE TO GO OR WHEN RETURNING BACK FROM WORSHIP PLACES.  There is intense hijacking & disappearance in progress from rides that are offered to people.                                                                                                                                                             
TAXI SERVICE:  It is noted UNREGISTERED VEHICLES arrive at places where there are large social gatherings, functions, bingos, etc, etc.  These Vehicles have been reported to be the vehicles of hijackers.
TRAVEL SAFE:  When Returning Home or Going To Any Place – ADHERE TO SAFE RULES AS GIVEN ABOVE.  THERE COULD BE VARIATIONS IN SITUATIONS / CIRCUMSTANCES, FOLLOW INTUTIVE JOURNEY
